# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __aexit__, __await__, __anext__ across all 14 asyncio subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 14 classes x 3 methods = 42 rows.
# __aexit__:  true for Timeout and TaskGroup; all others false.
# __await__:  true for Task and Future; all others false.
# __anext__:  true only for StreamReader; all others false.
# Lock/Semaphore/Condition/BoundedSemaphore inherit __aexit__ from a mixin —
# it is not in their own __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

